Others: The Baltimore Orioles will play against the Chicago White Sox on September 2, 2024.
The game is part of Childhood Cancer Awareness Month.
The Orioles will provide tickets to families of children who are currently being treated for cancer and who participated in the 2024 Maryland Trek.
An online auction featuring game-used memorabilia will benefit Just Power in Kids.
Hyundai Hope on Wheels will throw out the ceremonial first pitch.
The Baltimore Symphony Orchestra will perform the national anthem.
The Camden Franks will compete in the Berks Live Hot Dog Race.
